{"id":152403,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/中国茉莉花革命支持者快讯（第三期）：灌云血拆/","date":"2011-05-15T12:00:40Z","modified":"2011-05-15T12:00:40Z","title":"中国茉莉花革命支持者快讯（第三期）：灌云血拆","content":"<p><center></center></p>\n<div><span>江苏省连云港的茉莉花革命支持者来信请求我们将连云港市的灌云县列入茉莉花革命的散步市县。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日灌云县发生的暴力强拆事件让他们愤怒无比，<span>死者陆增罗被拆迁人员打死后，当局为了毁尸灭迹，点燃煤气罐引发大火，死者被烧得惨不忍睹。事后公安试图来抢尸，遭到家属和周边村民以菜刀和砖头抵抗，未能得逞。</span></span></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-n_-DZU-yX2A/Tc3_cakiYcI/AAAAAAAAAbE/HssxRCjieOc/s1600/05.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-n_-DZU-yX2A/Tc3_cakiYcI/AAAAAAAAAbE/HssxRCjieOc/s1600/05.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>邮件中称，灌云县委书记唐铁飞（连云港市委常委、灌云县委书记）自上任以来就自任土皇帝，十多年来，蔑视党纪国法，恶贯满盈，于今年年初离职。可是新任的县委书记鲁林（原连云港市政府副秘书长，市商务局局长）依旧延续唐铁飞的土皇帝作风，在没有得到江苏省国土厅批文的情况下，将上千亩土地非法出卖给开发商，并纵容暴力强拆等犯罪行为！灌云县小偷猖獗，基础建设异常落后，却得不到治理和改善。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>茉莉花革命的发起者与支持者响应灌云县的要求，用散步的方式聚集在一起，在强拆赤裸裸地变成恐怖血拆的今天，我们必须行动起来，揭露各地官员贪污腐败劣迹，并回到街头维护自己的权利！</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>时间：星期六下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span><span>点，星期天下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-9</span><span>点</span></div>\n<div><span>地点：灌云县富园广场步行街，伊山路交界处</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BIdcstcpHJM/Tc3_hKJyTWI/AAAAAAAAAbI/IwPyJYnY79k/s1600/01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"59\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BIdcstcpHJM/Tc3_hKJyTWI/AAAAAAAAAbI/IwPyJYnY79k/s320/01.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Df_NnIqrrPo/Tc3_hTlb9NI/AAAAAAAAAbM/4OXT1CiFwJY/s1600/02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"57\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Df_NnIqrrPo/Tc3_hTlb9NI/AAAAAAAAAbM/4OXT1CiFwJY/s320/02.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-pIQw2Igw0yw/Tc3_hlMUTFI/AAAAAAAAAbQ/lamTpg3-YBs/s1600/03.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"116\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-pIQw2Igw0yw/Tc3_hlMUTFI/AAAAAAAAAbQ/lamTpg3-YBs/s320/03.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lbaG6aYPJMw/Tc3_h4ajMKI/AAAAAAAAAbU/h4VSLxNTQ0U/s1600/04.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"107\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lbaG6aYPJMw/Tc3_h4ajMKI/AAAAAAAAAbU/h4VSLxNTQ0U/s320/04.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>江苏灌云县茉莉花革命支持者</span></div>\n<div><span>中国茉莉花革命发起者</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p>[中国茉莉花革命发起者 http://molihuaxingdong.blogspot.com] 转载请注明出处</p>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/3112334774117141878-7886663174059731639?l=molihuaxingdong.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":319,"categories":[1],"tags":[19306,15522,10562]}